  "title": "Air Freight Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Be the main contact for customers about shipping questions, bookings, and tracking.</li>\n  <li>Work with team members, carriers, and vendors to move cargo on time.</li>\n  <li>Solve customer complaints quickly to improve their experience.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and check shipping paperwork (like invoices and customs forms).</li>\n  <li>Keep an eye on shipments and update customers if anything changes.</li>\n  <li>Help with pricing and quotes for shipping services.</li>\n  <li>Keep customer records up to date in the system.</li>\n  <li>Follow all shipping laws, customs rules, and company guidelines.</li>\n  <li>Help the sales team with customer questions and support.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110980</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Lim Hooi Mei</p>",
